gw.plugin.vendormanagement

Class InvoiceAutomaticProcessingQualificationCheckResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.plugin.QualificationCheckResult
      • gw.plugin.vendormanagement.InvoiceAutomaticProcessingQualificationCheckResult

  • public class InvoiceAutomaticProcessingQualificationCheckResult
extends QualificationCheckResult
    Represents the result of the qualification check for a particular invoice-process action. Note that while DeclinedReasons will always be empty if the check was successful, it may also be empty if the check was not successful (i.e. declined): this simply indicates that it was declined without a specific reason.
